### <%= @class_header %> : slide_when_moving()
``` lua
local <%= @variable_text %>	-- example <%= @variable_text %>
<%= @variable_text %>:slide_when_moving( true )
```

If `true`, this <%= @class_name %> will slide to another <%= @link_tile %> when it moves, instead of teleporting.

#### Function Call
`<%= @variable_text %>:slide_when_moving( should_slide )`

#### Parameters
<%= @link_element %> `should_slide`<br>
	&emsp;If `true`, this <%= @class_name %> will slide between <%= @link_tile %>s when moving. Otherwise, it teleports.
